texts.text: v0.14.1 was an update to Minecraft: Pocket Edition that added skins from Minecraft: Story Mode. It was the last version to support iOS 5, 6, and 7.
Version exclusive: Minecraft Story Mode Skin Pack.
Loading in a world no longer displays the message "Generating World", and only the "Building Terrain" message.

10 issues fixed
From released versions before 0.14.0

MCPE-8162 – Tnt position not synced for clients
MCPE-10260 – Second skin layer does not show up correctly while crouching.
MCPE-11152 – Pink Sheep costume (halloween costumes skin pack) uses an incorrect player model
MCPE-11700 – Extra mushroom soup crafting recipe
MCPE-12393 – Fence gates sometimes don't open and sometimes don't shut

MCPE-13196 – Food continuous eating bug (when holding mouse right-click or touch hold down)
MCPE-13498 – Boat sinks into the solid blocks

Lighting glitches on all stair blocks have been fixed.
Renamed items are now used up when crafting with them.
